desc: Vista Finishing™ makes corbels, posts, crown molding and trim for CNC Cabinetry®. Pre-finished, color-matched and ready to install. Add WOW to your kitchen designs!

layout.text:
Vista Finishing™ offers wood hoods, corbels, molding and trim for stock cabinetry pre-finished in matching colors and ready to install.
Pair your cabinetry line with pre-finished details from Vista Finishing™ to create custom kitchen designs for less than custom or semi-custom cabinetry.
That's: Custom Within Reach™
Add Vista Finishing™ to your offering today!
